; Display warning message to the user
M291 P"Warning: Power to the Z-axis motors will be disconnected. Please remove any objects from under the bed. The bed will need to be manually lowered. Proceed carefully to avoid damage." R"Z-Axis Motor Power Off" S2 T0

; Disable the Z-axis motors to allow manual movement
M84 Z  ; Turn off power to the Z-axis motors

; Optional: Provide a final confirmation to the user
M291 P"The Z-axis motors have been powered off. Please manually lower the bed by hand." R"Manual Bed Lowering" S2 T0

